commit.message:
Implemented map searching capabilities to allow the user to navigate around the map

By clicking Z the user can now zoom in and out and move around the map
to get a better look at the hole. Clicking Z again brings the user back
to the set level of zoom and is centered back on the disc and ready to
throw again.

created cent holes and added collsion object with tree squares

Every tile 7 in any map created will now be a collsion object with
uniform height. Right now the code is commented out as the game runs too
slow for true gameplay while calculating collisions with every tree on
the map. Lines 76-79 need to be uncommented to bring this feature back.
